{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameNarration":"Kagome","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:Charles VII.@The king of France in this era.@Guided to his coronation by Jeanne La Pucelle,@he was recognized as the rightful king.]","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:Miss Melissa's father was angry@about the king's madness and@how La Pucelle was left to die...]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:He is crucial for uniting France.]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:However, seeing Charles VII up close,@he seems to be constantly trembling,@as if in fear...]"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story13","chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...I am troubled.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Should I proceed with military reforms despite the@nobles' resistance,"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"as Richemont suggests...?"},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"When I first met him, I sensed that he was@extraordinary."},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Moreover, he's unusually loyal for these times..."},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Leaving things to Richemont is a path toward@peace."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Yes...but I am afraid."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"My mother...that woman...Isabeau..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830200},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402301}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Perenelle","textCenter":"(Isabeau de Bavière is King Charles's actual@mother...)"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Perenelle","textCenter":"(King Charles has clashed with Isabeau multiple@times.)"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Perenelle","textCenter":"(He was even almost killed...)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"But Isabeau is no longer in this world."},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"The current events involve wars between people..."},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"The outcome will be determined by human nature@and the power of organizations, not unjust magic."},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"There are no monsters like that within the English@ranks anymore."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"I understand...@I understand, yet, I still have dreams..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"When I try to drive out England and achieve victory,"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"I have nightmares of that woman returning to@burn me alive..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"(Miss Isabeau's actions...really terrified him...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"(...Burned alive?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":402601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"(I have indeed witnessed Isabeau)"},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"(using such magic before.)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"(...But is it truly Isabeau the king fears?)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31121.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":100,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/4004_red_flame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.1},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":2,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3004_sparks.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.1},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":3,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/6002_sparks.ExportJson","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"autoTurnLast":0.1},{"chara":[{"id":402101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Tart","textCenter":"...@...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2,3],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":402601,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"...Your Majesty."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...What is it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"I know of a little magic that is effective against@nightmares."},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Please look into this child's eyes."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402601}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...What?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20121.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":1.0,"turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event05","nameNarration":"Dauphin Charles","narration":"\"Listen!\"","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20121.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"narration":"\"One and all!\""},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameRight":"Dauphin Charles","narrationEffect":"out","textBg":"shout","textRight":"This woman is a true maiden."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameRight":"Dauphin Charles","textBg":"shout","textRight":"A messenger of God!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":830100}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"That is...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":801100}],"nameLeft":"Bâtard","textLeft":"No way!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801100},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830100}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":1}]},{"chara":[{"id":830400,"lipSynch":0,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"nameRight":"Bâtard's Voice","textRight":"The Dauphin himself, welcoming his subjects..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830200}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Tart","textRight":"Gentle Dauphin!"},{"chara":[{"id":402101}],"nameRight":"Tart","textRight":"I have just come from Orleans...@And I am pleased to report that the French Army―"},{"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","chara":[{"id":830200,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Clasp*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"shake","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Tart","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"[chara:402101:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Charles","textCenter":"Enough. We have already heard!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":402101,"lipSynch":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Tart","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Charles","textCenter":"You have truly done a magnificent job, La Pucelle. "},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20122.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":830100}],"nameRight":"Gilles de Rais","textRight":"...Here is the holy oil.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402301},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402100,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"Noel!\"@(Hurray!)","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20122.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":402100}],"nameRight":"Tart","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Gentle Dauphin... No, Your Majesty."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":402100}],"textRight":"Congratulation on your coronation!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":1.0,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...La Pucelle...","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"You remembered...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"La Pucelle reclaimed Orleans,"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"and bestowed upon me the true crown."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Yet, I...when she was captured..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"I could do nothing...I stood idly by..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Not only that, I even forgot about her existence..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Your Majesty..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...What?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Perhaps what you truly feared was not your mother,"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"but rather your own sense of guilt...?"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"The guilt for not being able to save Tart...La Pucelle,"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"and leaving her to die..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Could that be the source of your nightmares...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Oh..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...That might be true."},{"chara":[{"id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"La Pucelle was a messenger of God, a true saint."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Yet...she was executed as a heretic,"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"a witch that misled people..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"I should have never turned a blind eye to it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402601}],"nameCenter":"Melissa & Elisa","textCenter":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402301},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402601}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome & Torte","textCenter":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001},{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"At the very least, I must restore her...her honor..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"lipSynch":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"...!"},{"chara":[{"id":402301,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"Then at the church...can we redo Tart's trial?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Skipping ahead like that is beyond my power@as a king of worldly things."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Furthermore..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Rouen, where the inquisition took place,@is under English control."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Right now, I can't even investigate the legitimacy@of the trial."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"...Yes...that's true."},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"However...once we reclaim Rouen..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"Lord Charles...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Yes, I promise. I will do my utmost"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"for the restoration of La Pucelle's honor."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"We did it, Miss Melissa!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":1,"tear":1}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"Yes...!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameNarration":"Kagome","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:Miss Melissa, who was very devoted,@was so happy that it made me@happy just by watching her.]","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:Miss Elisa said it wouldn't save Miss Jeanne...@But she seemed a little happy@that it would help her remaining@family and comrades.]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:The change in the king's heart that@occurred in the realm of his mind@should gradually lead the real world of@the mid-15th century in a better direction.]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:And that made me realize:@The tragedy of Jeanne La Pucelle has twisted@the lives of the people left behind...@That's truly a sad thing.]"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
